July 28, 2017 7:30 PM ET
Internet Software and Services

Company Overview of General Motors Financial of Canada Limited



Snapshot People




Company Overview
General Motors Financial of Canada Limited, doing business as FinanciaLinx, develops online dealer solutions. It offers an Internet-based credit approval system for car dealers, which allows them to have their credit approved in under two minutes. General Motors Financial of Canada Limited was formerly known as AmeriCredit Financial Services of Canada Ltd. The company was founded in 1998 and is based in Toronto, Canada. General Motors Financial of Canada Limited operates as a subsidiary of General Motors Financial Company, Inc.


2001 Sheppard Avenue EastSuite 600Toronto, ON M2J 4Z8CanadaFounded in 1998



Phone: 416-753-4000

Fax: 416-753-4100

www.gmfinancial.ca







